{"tid":2409914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12.22愛丁堡廣場聲援維吾爾族人權集會 3男被控暴動 2人不認罪明年開審 1人認罪放棄保釋 還押候判","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T15:31:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd11ade22271b7b7d064751410e1050c67a10051","tid":2409914,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13664&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=53da36bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13664</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿七庭<br />\n#高勁修首席區域法院法官<br />\n#1222中環 #提訊 <br />\n<br />\nA1陸(20)<br />\nA2梁(21)<br />\nA3蕭(21) <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1.暴動 （所有被告）<br />\n2.意圖妨礙拘捕或檢控罪犯而協助罪犯 （A1）<br />\n3.襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員 （A3）<br />\n4.襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員 （A2） <br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n三人被控於2019年12月22日，在中環愛丁堡廣場 5 號大會堂低座外，連同其他身份不詳的人士參與暴動；A1另被控於同日同地，在A3襲擊執行職務的警務人員後，知悉或相信A3有罪時，把已被警員53734制服的A3拉走，意圖妨礙拘捕或檢控A3。（控罪一及二）<br />\nA2、3則分別被控於同日同地襲擊正在正當執行職務的高級督察34135及警員58747（控罪三、四） <br />\n<br />\nA1、3皆不認罪❌<br />\nA2就控罪1及4認罪❗️ <br />\n<br />\nA2將於2021年5月18日 1100 聽取答辯及求情，期間放棄保釋，需要還押‼️ <br />\n<br />\n控方將傳召13名警員及1名市民作為證人，沒有警戒供詞，但有25段片段，需要播放的片段約有1小時46分。<br />\n<br />\nA1,A3案件將終押後至2022年2月24日 0930 區域法院進行審前覆核，正審將於2022年3月14日至18日進行，審期5天，兩人以現有條件保釋。"},{"pid":"d7dedec4df7a6646386461c592fbd067b46999d5","tid":2409914,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6cee8907bc24d2ef7dcdc3b12d660a03e70ca2","tid":2409914,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac201dd038bf5bacf80b1f25e586721d1e6ed3d","tid":2409914,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0957f2e183a5a8b636f077b07806d34171074310","tid":2409914,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:10:01.000Z","msg":"普通襲擊都暴動"},{"pid":"1165bb746b2df4b94ae046081f0c2f756a201e31","tid":2409914,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:14:32.000Z","msg":"暴動最少都要三年起跳 唉"},{"pid":"14b805b2c65a0438bd56070be82ee25355db0b75","tid":2409914,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:17:14.000Z","msg":"市民前年12月在愛丁堡廣場舉行「聲援維吾爾族人權集會」，其間警方與示威者發生衝突。當日有學生被指踢高級督察的背部，隨即被捕；及後有示威者疑拉著該學生的背囊，以阻止警員拘捕學生，另有青年涉推撞現場一名警長。案件今在區域法院再訊時，涉推撞警長的青年表明打算認罪，並主動提出撤銷保釋，還柙至今年5月正式答辯。至於另外兩名被告則不認罪，將於明年3月受審。<br />\n<br />\n梁今透過代表大狀表明擬承認暴動及襲警罪，並主動提出放棄保釋。首席法官高勁修押後其案件至5月18日正式聽取答辯，其間梁須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n而蕭及陸則表明不認罪，他們的案件押後至明年3月14日開審，審期預計5天。蕭另被控一項襲警罪，控罪指他於同日同地襲擊在正當執行職務的高級督察A。控方早前修改控罪詳情，披露高級督察編號為34135。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/XRZ6T45PH5DY3OIWPLJGQOINCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FXRZ6T45PH5DY3OIWPLJGQOINCM%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BmHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=09c20edb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FXRZ6T45PH5DY3OIWPLJGQOINCM%2F&h=66c752bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/XRZ6T45PH5DY3OIWPLJGQOINCM/</a>"},{"pid":"34fba752c20fe71a65660a7cc11b332b20ea143d","tid":2409914,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"根本當日乜都冇，普通襲警，咁都暴動"},{"pid":"8ca8af57eb4ebd293a133f55b55af965250f05eb","tid":2409914,"uid":271513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"頂係啲狗衝入來打人<br />\n<br />\n狗曱暴動就有"},{"pid":"974e5f42030def0841573302d7e2c8cbacfec01f","tid":2409914,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1370fafed9886a67e13a921abd0e24d64c2d2af","tid":2409914,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d8b49f73221928c7ae1924523a4040da52d6280","tid":2409914,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"cls, 老屈，濫捕"},{"pid":"ccabfb3eafe3503b354bb7c1c52db9b84d894af2","tid":2409914,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9b3a492f2f45f873fa1a4f001487c9ded105e3","tid":2409914,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0957f2e183a5a8b636f077b07806d34171074310","tid":2409914,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T10:10:01.000Z","msg":"普通襲擊都暴動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />暴動個門檻就黎低到好似食飯咁"},{"pid":"f40b2815a878e3ca2c4b556e58a826b08aa653b2","tid":2409914,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b9b3a492f2f45f873fa1a4f001487c9ded105e3",